                    <span>This book must have been obsolete already 7 years ago. DOS there is the most popular system, assembler is still 16-bit, with some "news" on few pages about "new" 32-bit one. It is ridiculous how they can annotate this book as up-to-date and for such ski-high price ! Don't fall in this trap.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Easy to read and very helpful.</div>
